nguard.com/news/sweetlab-deploys-half-million-water-filters-in-rwanda/\">\"SWEETLab deploys half million water filters in Rwanda\"</a>. <i>Portland State Vanguard</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2015-04-21</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Portland+State+Vanguard&amp;rft.atitle=SWEETLab+deploys+half+million+water+filters+in+Rwanda&amp;rft.date=2015-02-23&amp;rft.aulast=Thiebes&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fpsuvanguard.com%2Fnews%2Fsweetlab-deploys-half-million-water-filters-in-rwanda%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALifeStraw\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Friend, Gil. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.worldchanging.com/archives/003388.html\">\"The LifeStraw\"</a>. <i>Worldchanging - Evaluation + Tools + Best Practices</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2015-04-21</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Worldchanging+-+Evaluation+%2B+Tools+%2B+Best+Practices&amp;rft.atitle=The+LifeStraw&amp;rft.aulast=Friend&amp;rft.aufirst=Gil&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldchanging.com%2Farchives%2F003388.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALifeStraw\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vestergaard-frandsen.com/lifestraw/lifestraw/longevity-and-efficacy\">Longevity and Efficacy</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20110129155546/http://www.vestergaard-frandsen.com/lifestraw/lifestraw/longevity-and-efficacy\">Archived</a> 2011-01-29 at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/19121634/site/newsweek/page/0/\">Water for The World</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/MSNBC\" title=\"MSNBC\">MSNBC</a>, By Jennie Yabroff,\n6/12/07.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vestergaard-frandsen.com/component/content/article/38-lifestraw/128-does-lifestraw-remove-parasites-like-cryptosporidium-and-giardia\">\"Vestergaard - Impacting People\"</a>. <i>www.vestergaard-frandsen.com</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=www.vestergaard-frandsen.com&amp;rft.atitle=Vestergaard+-+Impacting+People&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vestergaard-frandsen.com%2Fcomponent%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2F38-lifestraw%2F128-does-lifestraw-remove-parasites-like-cryptosporidium-and-giardia&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALifeStraw\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://lifestraw.com/faqs/\">\"LifeStraw - We make contaminated water safe to drink\"</a>. <i>LifeStraw</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_va